summary
=======

(*) Since version 3.10 you are able to add a link to Account
    Administration block (see CHANGELOG for details).
    
(*) Since version 3.11 last login is displayed (enabled by default).

(*) Since version 3.11.3 GeoIP based suspicious login prevention is
    available (pwtools plugin is required). Release requires re-configuration.
    Credits go to freegeoip.net for providing free GeoIP services.
    IMPORTANT: Add "nosummary" to main configuration "dont_override" key in
               order to disallow bypassing of GeoIP based suspicious login
               prevention.
               
(*) Version 3.14 requires reconfiguration. 
